==Latin==
===Etymology===
A modern [[neologism]] based on translating [[World Wide Web]].  [[world|World]] as [[terra]]; [[wide]], in the sense of "all" the world, as [[totus]]; [[web]] as [[tela]]).  The triple [[alliteration]] is kept, but in "T" not "W".
#: ''Latinitas in tela totius terrae'' &mdash; grexlat.com [http://www.grexlat.com/]
===Proper noun===
# [[World Wide Web]].